		<th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" height="25" width="100">&nbsp;Author</th><th class="PanelHeader" align="Left" width="85%">&nbsp;Thread: What to do when you have a Shammy and Chanter in group?</th>
	</tr><tr>
		<td class="PanelBody" nowrap="nowrap" valign="Top" width="150"><table border="0">
			<tr>
				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Sinfonian is not online. Last active: 3/2/2004 8:47:31 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Sinfonian">Sinfonian</a><br><a class="SmallText" href="http://www.eqdiva.com" target="_new">www.eqdiva.com</a></td>
