				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What to do when you have a Shammy and Chanter in group?<a name="5575"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 20 03 8:32 AM</span></td>
