				<td colspan="2"><span>
<br />
If the important areas are covered, and the DPS comes
<br />
more from nuking/pet classes than melees, here's something
<br />
I enjoy doing.  Mind you, this is with drums of the beast,
<br />
which is equippable in primary while weilding another weapon.
<br />

<br />
Load up the 4 DoT songs.
<br />

<br />
Keep your drums on your cursor, and start twisting away
<br />
the dots while meleeing.  When your dot is about to land,
<br />
click in the drums for full damage, and then click back in
<br />
your weapon.  You will be amazed by your now superior
<br />
DPS.  I was grouped with a pally, 2 wizards and a mage last
<br />
night, and until I explained what I was doing, their impression
<br />
was that &quot;this used to be a lot harder&quot;.
<br />

<br />
Astuce Subterfuge</span></td>
