				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: What to do when you have a Shammy and Chanter in group?<a name="6365"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 16 03 12:38 PM</span></td>
